.TH "meson_spifc_txrx" 9 "meson_spifc_txrx" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
meson_spifc_txrx \- transfer a chunk of data
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" meson_spifc_txrx
.BI "(struct meson_spifc *spifc "  ","
.BI "struct spi_transfer *xfer "  ","
.BI "int offset "  ","
.BI "int len "  ","
.BI "bool last_xfer "  ","
.BI "bool last_chunk "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "spifc" 12
the Meson SPI device
.IP "xfer" 12
the current SPI transfer
.IP "offset" 12
offset of the data to transfer
.IP "len" 12
length of the data to transfer
.IP "last_xfer" 12
whether this is the last transfer of the message
.IP "last_chunk" 12
whether this is the last chunk of the transfer
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, a negative value on error
